{"word":"H650 - אָפִיק - ʼâphîyq - aw-feek' - Brook","slug":"H650","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָפִיק</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼâphîyq"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-feek'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Brook"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05E4;&#x05D9;&#x05E7; - 'a&#x0302;ph&#x0131;&#x0302;yq</b> - <i>aw-feek'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H622\">H622</a>; properly <i>containing</i>, that is, a <i>tube</i>; also a <i>bed</i> or <i>valley</i> of a stream; also a <i>strong</i> thing or a <i>hero: - </i>brook, channel, mighty, river, + scale, stream, strong piece."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H662\">H662</a>, <a href=\"#/H663\">H663</a>, <a href=\"#/H664\">H664</a>"}]}